# Reference: https://github.com/CMU-SAFARI/ramulator2
Follow these steps to get Ramulator as part of XS-GEM5

1.Download Ramulator2
    1.1  Go to ext/ramulator2 (this directory)
    1.2  Clone Ramulator2: git@github.com:CMU-SAFARI/ramulator2.git
    1.3  cd ramulator2 && mkdir build
    1.4  cmake ..
    1.5  make -j


2. Compile gem5
    2.1 cd gem5
    2.2 Business as usual

